The paper focuses on the problem of script identification in natural images, which is a subfield of computer vision (cs.CV). The proposed method also involves the use of a Naive-Bayes Nearest Neighbor classifier, which is a common technique in natural language processing (cs.CL). The paper also mentions the importance of automatic text understanding systems, which falls under information retrieval (cs.IR). The proposed method involves the use of convolutional features, which is a common technique in machine learning (cs.LG).
